How to Uncover a Lie
A look at the current headlines shows how thoughtful and widespread deception and lies are in everyday life.
The Republican presidential candidate, Herman Cain, is engaged in becoming the master of the accusations of sexual harassment on the part of several women. Both sides accuse each other of lying.
Penn State's leadership is accused of perjury, as reportedly held back reports after which a retired football coach had sexually abused a boy.
